# Assets Immediate Borrower Claims

## identifier
de8746

## type
float

## definition
This is the value, as at the relevant date, for immediate borrower claims representing all on-balance sheet financial claims, excluding derivative contracts and lending of securities, gold and other precious metals without cash collateral.

## syntax
### xbrl
- balance=debit
- name=Assets.ClaimsCrossBorder.Amount
- classification=baf/bafpo/bafpo1.02.06
- period=instant
